.span12.section.no-border.examples
  %h3 What Are People Using It For?
  .row
    .span4
      %a.logo{:href => "http://news.hnkansai.org"}
        %img{:src => "images/hnkansai.png"}
      / %h4 Community Site             
      %p The <a href="http://news.hnkansai.org">Hacker News Kansai</a> community uses Telescope to keep in touch and share ideas in between meetups. 
    .span4  
      %a.logo{:href => "http://sidebar.io"}
        %img{:src => "images/sidebar.png"}
      / %h4 Collaborative Linkblog
      %p <a href="http://sidebar.io">Sidebar</a> uses Telescope's digest view to display the 5 best design links of the day, as curated by a team of editors. 
    .span4
      %a.logo{:href => "http://www.leakmap.com"}
        %img{:src => "images/leakmap.png"}
      / %h4 Feature Roadmap
      %p <a href="http://www.leakmap.com">Leakmap</a> is a dynamic roadmap for Meteor features that lets users vote on the feature they'd most like to see built next. 
